.B
\fBhasBackgroundColour(This) -> boolean() when This :: wxTextAttr().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns true if the attribute object specifies a background colour.


.RE
.B
\fBhasFont(This) -> boolean() when This :: wxTextAttr().\fR

.br
.RS
