.br
.RS
.PP
Sets the paragraph alignment.

.PP
See ?wxTextAttrAlignment enumeration values.

.PP
Of these, wxTEXT_ALIGNMENT_JUSTIFIED is unimplemented. In future justification may be supported when printing or previewing, only.


.RE
.B
\fBsetBackgroundColour(This, ColBack) -> ok\fR
\fB                             when\fR
\fB                                 This :: wxTextAttr(),\fR
\fB                                 ColBack :: wx:wx_colour().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Sets the background colour.


.RE
.B
\fBsetFlags(This, Flags) -> ok\fR
\fB                  when This :: wxTextAttr(), Flags :: integer().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Sets the flags determining which styles are being specified.

.PP
The ?wxTextAttrFlags values can be passed in a bitlist.


.RE
.B
\fBsetFont(This, Font, [Option]) -> ok\fR
\fB                 when\fR
\fB                     This :: wxTextAttr(),\fR
\fB                     Font :: wxFont:wxFont(),\fR
\fB                     Option :: {flags, integer()}.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Sets the attributes for the given font.

.PP
