\fBsetTextColour(This, ColText) -> ok\fR
\fB                       when\fR
\fB                           This :: wxTextAttr(),\fR
\fB                           ColText :: wx:wx_colour().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Sets the text foreground colour.


.RE
